rows.label: tev026501_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Regina about her shop.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Regina if anything is troubling her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0001
rows.name:
We sell strange and unusual stuff my husband picks
up out on the job. He's a Pathfinder, so he's always
finding crazy space junk and whatnot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0002
rows.name:
I don't have anything to show you right now,
unfortunately, but check back later.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0003
rows.name:
He should be back in a little while with a new haul
that'll blow your battle socks clean off![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0008
rows.name: Yes, actually.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0009
rows.name:
But I'm not going to talk about it. I don't even want to
entertain the possibility of it being true.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0010
rows.name:
I'm just going to stay positive and hold on to hope.
So please don't ask again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Regina about the church.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Regina about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0011
rows.name:
My husband and I were planning to have a proper
wedding at this church.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0012
rows.name:
After we lost contact with him, I came here every
single night to pray he'd make it home alive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0013
rows.name: But I guess...God didn't hear me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0014
rows.name: Maybe Mira's just out of earshot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0018
rows.name:
It sounds like our shop's doing well under new
ownership. My BLADE friends still say there's no other
establishment that can compete.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0019
rows.name:
I dropped by the other day just to take a peek.
A Ma-non named Giogion was pulling in all kinds of
new customers. What a hard worker![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0020
rows.name:
I was ready to clonk him one on the head if he
tanked the business and drove my hubby's reputation
into the ground.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev026501_MSG0021
rows.name:
But it seems like he's doing a good job.
It really takes a load off my shoulders.[ST:wait ]
